snippet.title: Nintendo Switch 『Miracle Snack Shop』 Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Official Website : https://www.cfk.kr/miracle/en.php

An ordinary snack shop cook meets a queen from another... world?!

The story-driven game developer Talesshop's masterpiece
『Miracle Snack Shop』 is coming to Nintendo Switch!

A love story as sweet as shaved ice, and as sentimental as a drama!
Coming this year on Nintendo Switch!
